Optional external TTS support:

StackChan Minimal may be configured to connect to external TTS servers, including piper-plus and a user-provided VOICEVOX-compatible adapter.

This repository does not include VOICEVOX, VOICEVOX Engine, VOICEVOX Core, voice models, voice libraries, or VOICEVOX installers.

When using generated audio from VOICEVOX voice libraries, users must follow the VOICEVOX software terms and each voice library's terms.

